{"tid":2100871,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【罪大滔天】逼站據報擬本港上市","createTime":"2020-07-09T10:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T16:59:12.000Z","uid":51665,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f0b7daaa9772dfaea7f0309b122ce21f22b08378","tid":2100871,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:55:05.000Z","msg":"【Now財經台】傳內地影音網站嗶哩嗶哩計劃來港第二上市，不過公司不予置評。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》引述知情人士指，阿里巴巴(09988)和騰訊(00700)有持股的嗶哩嗶哩，因為中美關係緊張，將仿傚其他中概股回流本港掛牌，公司已經與投資銀行初步商討。<br />\n<br />\n消息又指公司計劃，發行5%至10%股份，不過，因為要符合第二上市要求，公司最快要明年才能在港上市。<br />\n<br />\n嗶哩嗶哩2018年在美國納斯達克掛牌，目前市值超過160億美元，股價年初至今已累升1.5倍。<br />\n<br />\n逼站呢條仆街俾美帝踢走死心不息想嚟香港掠水續命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有乜辦法可以送佢一程<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c8898ee4ab6d8ad304abe5277a0445bded7e41","tid":2100871,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:56:43.000Z","msg":"共享大彎區殊榮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dO8B1ts.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdO8B1ts.jpg&h=ce92fd0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34d3f69eaa2963fa9090dc26b0b77db73e810782","tid":2100871,"uid":79117,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:57:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab98aef8db2acb508af2bcc13c5be6e522261123","tid":2100871,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"支持b站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9bd0b1a1e7d3c376005f9d86e9f4684e46d47e","tid":2100871,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:02:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bc5f0381b02dc614e448064bd5e3197bde4ff499","tid":2100871,"uid":25367,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"34d3f69eaa2963fa9090dc26b0b77db73e810782","tid":2100871,"uid":79117,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:57:34.000Z",